I"»<p>Early decisions made by Councils about the regeneration of council estates go under the radar, discouraging resident involvement.</p>

<p><a href="">This</a> script runs once a week, scraping the websites of all 33 London boroughs searching for the following keywords and displaying the results below - (estate OR renewal OR regeneration OR demolition OR redevelopment).</p>

